{"tid":1423454,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"我作為一個土生土長的香港人","createTime":"2019-08-06T13:58:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-06T14:19:46.000Z","uid":239472,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"346dd47cf53cca0a183413a50c5ae0695d56763b","tid":1423454,"uid":239472,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T13:58:31.000Z","msg":"餐廳最近發生了很多事﹐我作為一個土生土長的香港人﹐看到那麼多貪心與自私感到痛心。一個人的口味不能代表他人﹐就像一小間只偏袒某遊客生意的店舖不能代表全部餐廳。飲食業已經發展多於64年了﹐食物安全品質是餐廳的一部份﹐我是客人這一點無需多言。我不認同也不支持所有自私的人和事﹐希望餐廳盡快恢復食物質素。<br />\n<br />\n因為他們貪心﹐為了錢令他們自身質素變得差劣﹐也令我肚子作出抗議了。因為我實在無法拍下肚子抗議後的照片，太令人嘔心了，最後只能夠畫出來。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>#五星級食物有140000慢人污其手<br />\n#屙屎污其手</strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gMY9K7S.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgMY9K7S.png&h=3ec4d897&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"25b9bc9dc03b7425070c8096fd94b72c7819ebf7","tid":1423454,"uid":239472,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T14:02:07.000Z","msg":"輕鬆一下 大家最近都攰了<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d9d20ad91cf1e6b4d43a09e42506249f2a132a9","tid":1423454,"uid":239472,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T14:09:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b908518ee6e8ec41bbda4d587e21ae533b7ff010","tid":1423454,"uid":239472,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T14:19:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}